* To start the implementation, let's define the necessary global variables...
*
*  @code{.c}
*  task LED_Task; /*The task node*/
*  stateMachine LED_FSM; /*The state -machine handle*/
*  sm::state State_LEDOff, State_LEDOn, State_LEDBlink;
*  @endcode 
